node.text:
The Tune Squad is back with two limited-edition Space Jam: A New Legacy all-terrain clogs with Jibbitz™ charms! 🏀 Available tomorrow at 12 pm EST at Crocs.com. Swipe to see how to purchase!​ Also available in select stores while supplies last.

UPDATE: Space Jam: A New Legacy crocs are sold out online but are still available in select stores while supplies last. ​
